extracurriculars.title: Founder & CEO
extracurriculars.description:
Founded an AI-driven education company that has successfully prepared over 100 students across North America for prestigious mathematics competitions, including AMC, AIME, USAMO, and USAJMO.

Key Achievements:

• Student Impact: Successfully prepared 100+ students across North America for top-tier math competitions
• Revenue Growth: Generated $75,000+ total revenue with MRR of $5,000-$10,000 
• Recognition: Featured on the front cover of BCBusiness, Oak Bay News, and CheqNews

Platform Development:

• Teaching Experience: Leveraged 150+ hours of direct instruction and extensive independent training background
• Technology Integration: Built proprietary platform with automated scheduling, payment processing, and communication tools
AI Innovation: Integrated AI-driven curriculum development for personalized learning experiences
• Scalability: Designed an automated ecosystem for rapid expansion and enhanced student outcomes

Team & Partnerships:

• Expert Faculty: Assembled team of 10 coaches affiliated with prestigious universities (MIT, UC Berkeley, CMU)
• Geographic Reach: Established North America-wide student base and coaching network

conversation_history.content: Hi Ethan! If you could fast forward to 2-5 years from now, what long term goal / goals do you have? This could be anything from getting accepted into a dream university, launching your own startup, or becoming a successful practitioner in a field you're passionate about.
I want to get into a top 10 university

Great! I can see you're focused on top 10 university acceptance. Would you like to share some of your extracurricular activities and experiences that relate to these goals? This will help me give you more targeted advice.
Yes, I'd like to share my extracurriculars
Perfect! Please add your extracurricular activities one at a time. For each activity, provide a title and description.

Counselor: Wow, Ethan, your achievements with the AI-driven education company are truly impressive! Founding a company that has such a significant impact on students and being featured in major publications is no small feat. Given your strong entrepreneurial background and tech expertise, there's a unique opportunity that could really set you apart in your university applications. 

Would you be interested in exploring how you could leverage your AI and education platform to develop a collaborative project with a university lab or professor? This could not only enhance your application but also provide you with valuable insights and connections in the academic world.
